This topic is the subject of an IETF working group called IPSEC (IP Security).
There are:

   - a mailing list available at ipsec-request@ans.net
   - an archive of the mailing list, available by ftp from ftp.ans.net in
     ~pub/archive/ipsec
   - various proposals in the form of draft internet RFC's

